/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燒咗就即係一D生態價值都無<br />\n過多排就批俾恒基<br />\nfat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲下燒哂郊野公園 污染成個香港海域<br />\n就可以伐林填海造地"},{"pid":"0f76cb97680a8a8942d2d2e19a567447ff0d6530","tid":591562,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5eb3373e8b8d77bfda9c8c4b3c570ddff28454ab","tid":591562,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e45fe9230a85584c867fd80c43e1d9da8814c028","tid":591562,"uid":117651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"畀人縱火，咁啱閉路電視都壞撚晒，真係好慘啊發展商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}